    "description": "玩家可以操纵主人公“莫里斯”在城市里转悠，与多个NPC对话，与钢琴等各种事物相互作用。游戏的主要内容是，欣赏迷你游戏和冒险，以及在重要瞬间登场的视频动画，了解莫里斯的故事。为了帮助主人公叙事的投入，还准备了20种以上的迷你游戏和配角角色的叙事和收集要素等丰富游戏的内容。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129160/extras/66cdcbd204ac3d3cead5b81c1945aeda.poster.avif?t=1729549375\" width=610 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129160/extras/66cdcbd204ac3d3cead5b81c1945aeda.webm?t=1729549375\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129160/extras/66cdcbd204ac3d3cead5b81c1945aeda.mp4?t=1729549375\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >冒险和主人公的叙事</h2>玩家成为埃文斯城的钢琴家莫里斯，通过与多个NPC及事物的相互作用进行游戏。<br>通过与不同人物的对话，体验一下爵士乐钢琴家莫里斯的故事吧。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129160/extras/f403fef34364a3a1e0d8d1a8e6cd902c.poster.avif?t=1729549375\" width=610 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129160/extras/f403fef34364a3a1e0d8d1a8e6cd902c.webm?t=1729549375\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129160/extras/f403fef34364a3a1e0d8d1a8e6cd902c.mp4?t=1729549375\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >迷你游戏</h2>为了帮助叙事投入，提供符合主人公多种行动的小游戏。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129160/extras/1bfa6c8cf6ff5b95cae0dfd151331617.poster.avif?t=1729549375\" width=610 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129160/extras/1bfa6c8cf6ff5b95cae0dfd151331617.webm?t=1729549375\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129160/extras/1bfa6c8cf6ff5b95cae0dfd151331617.mp4?t=1729549375\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >有着独特故事的各种各样的人物。</h2>配角们都有各自的叙事。故事将根据与配角角色对话时的选项和主人公的叙事会有所不同。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >活动与探险</h2>访问城市中的各个场所，和角色对话，收集收藏品吧～！<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>乐谱</li></ul>在关键时刻慎重的选择。根据选择的结果，可以收集可以演奏的乐谱。探戈和巴萨诺瓦、酷爵士、现代爵士乐等，请亲自在游戏中进行的节奏游戏中进行比赛。<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>珍贵的唱片们</li></ul>帮助其他人解决烦恼，或者翻看乐器店后面堆积的老唱片等。通过在埃文斯城的多种相互作用，收集罕见的唱片吧。<br>收集多种类型的唱片，在主人公的房间通过转盘在游戏中欣赏！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129160/extras/5a5e9b6aaefb9a6b6ee3c03138a5eaaa.poster.avif?t=1729549375\" width=610 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129160/extras/5a5e9b6aaefb9a6b6ee3c03138a5eaaa.webm?t=1729549375\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129160/extras/5a5e9b6aaefb9a6b6ee3c03138a5eaaa.mp4?t=1729549375\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129160/extras/574a5432aa864a3fde0023ff1c67f9a8.poster.avif?t=1729549375\" width=610 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129160/extras/574a5432aa864a3fde0023ff1c67f9a8.webm?t=1729549375\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129160/extras/574a5432aa864a3fde0023ff1c67f9a8.mp4?t=1729549375\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><i>充满故事和音乐的经历<br>请体验爵士乐钢琴家的莫里斯的故事。《爵士星期三》提供了爵士乐、爱情和失败带来的梦幻体验。</i><br><br><strong>喜欢这款游戏的话，一定要收藏哦！我们会继续努力为您展现更优质的游戏！</strong>",
